			<CASNumber>7647-14-5</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Sodium chloride, commonly known as salt, is an ionic compound with the chemical formula NaCl, representing a 1:1 ratio of sodium and chloride ions. It is the salt most responsible for the salinity of seawater and of the extracellular fluid of many multicellular organisms. It is an essential nutrient and is used in healthcare to help prevent patients from becoming dehydrated. It is used as a food preservative and as a seasoning to enhance flavor. Sodium chloride is also used in manufacturing to make plastics and other products, and it is used to de-ice roads and sidewalks.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氯化钠俗称食盐，是一种离子化合物，化学式为 NaCl，钠离子和氯离子的比例为 1:1。它是海水和许多多细胞生物体细胞外液含盐量最高的盐。它是人体必需的营养物质，在医疗保健中用于防止病人脱水。它还被用作食品防腐剂和调味料，以增加风味。氯化钠还用于制造塑料和其他产品，并用于道路和人行道除冰。</common:generalComment>
